{
  "stem": "27409.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I couldn't leave because my director and the other higher in rank and the credit inspector in the [INAUDIBLE] army.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Had to join the army.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was slept with the other five and the money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we went the direction, were directed in direction of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That is on the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I we crossed there in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There were peasants, which were forced to, with their carriages, to bring us on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We crossed the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was night.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "During the day they-- usually the German bomb, the Stukas, across in the night of [INAUDIBLE] and continued.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there were some Russian soldiers which directed us in this direction to go.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We didn't realize.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Suddenly, I recognized their German uniforms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We enter and the Russians are encircled-- the German encircled us in their tank units.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And the-- the so-called Russian guides, they're German in Russian uniforms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Immediately, they closed and said in rows to stay.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And it was immediately two hours of this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They're standing not knowing what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Yes, in the October war, which created, I set fire to the money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] not to [INAUDIBLE] the enemy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But I was in [INAUDIBLE] to escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "It was still dark, and I heard the shout, [? commissary, ?] commissars and Jews [GERMAN] to come forward.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I say, it's not for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "So I tried, and I succeeded in escaping in the direction to the west I was marching.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I succeeded crossing the [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Niesse ?] in the other direction.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I got rid of my uniform, hid as a peasant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And a lot of peasant then driven by the German over to the west for forced labor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "When I came in the other side, I knew more or less the region, and knew my direction, tried to get home.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
